title: Ingersoll Lockwood - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 2/18/22
itunes:title: Ingersoll Lockwood - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 2/18/22
description:
Guest host Richard Syrett and authors Walter Bosley and Todd Wood discuss the works of obscure novelist Ingersoll Lockwood, whose little known novels written in the 1890s seem to predict the life of former President Donald Trump and his son Baron.
